<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB">MS: I have to pass Llodra first and he is a very tricky player.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>
